{
  "stem": "5626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's when they started to apart from us, and we really were-- were say, frozen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was inducted in the armed services first time, 1940.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he came home after six months because one of the law let him come home because he had two children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was called back again, 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since he was a shoemaker, he didn't serve with weapon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was the shoemaker in the armed services.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was there until 1944, the time I was inducted into the services.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saw my father after this, 1945, August, end of August.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew where he went, to the service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But further, we didn't know which city or what group he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And two years after I was through with my learning of the trade, I was working in a-- a small factory, which owned by the Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was working over there in 1944, May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's when I was inducted into the service.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have to jump back for about a good month. 1944, March 19.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The German army occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they occupied the capital city of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was in a theater, in a matinee show in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the president of the theater came out and says that the program which was scheduled to go on now, for a reason which we are not telling you people, cannot be shown.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we will play something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a different show.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the intermission we went out to the balcony and looked on the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw the motorcycle, the side-sitter motorcycles full of German SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when the occupation started.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
